    "# Conducting a systematic spatial scene search over a large region using ***pyeodh***\n",
    "* **Other useful documentation:** https://docs.eodatahub.org.uk/Analysts/APIs/api-examples/#spatial-search\n",
    "* **EODH data catalogue link:** https://eodatahub.org.uk/static-apps/sg-rc-ui/prod/index.html#/\n",
    "\n",
    "<div style=\"background-color:#e6f2ff; padding:10px; border-left:5px solid #1f77b4;\">\n",
    "<strong>Prerequisites</strong>\n",
    "<ol>\n",
    "<li> Define a set of grid squares over the regional Area Of Interest (AOI), which will be used for a programmatic, systematic scene search in this script. You will need the coordinates of the bounding box for that grid square\n",
    "<li> Briefly browse the EODH data catalogue to discover what data collections are available to search\n",
    "</li>\n",
    "</ol>\n",
    "</div>"
   ]
  },
